            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.branch",
                    "sections": [
                        {
                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                            "expression": {
                                "type": "expressions.hasActiveQuest",
                                "propId": "6fdd5328-909a-40a3-8b6a-5d9feae40b4d",
                                "sceneId": "e8520824-d970-4c6e-8aec-6c308c8846ab",
                                "questStatus": "0"
                            },
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.quests",
                                    "id": "d34ecad1-0f92-4349-94b4-784d1cabcddc",
                                    "sceneId": "e8520824-d970-4c6e-8aec-6c308c8846ab",
                                    "propId": "6fdd5328-909a-40a3-8b6a-5d9feae40b4d",
                                    "target": "2",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "02694963-1ae7-43c3-a089-d7c19699ef8f",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Welcome back, Shawn. We hoped that you would again join us.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "524f6c22-7164-4bd4-8e84-ab8f6135f494",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "974c1c05-d050-48b8-b36b-1ddcdde5e230",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today, we shall put that Information about Alchemy and Enchantment from yesterday's lesson to practical use by creating a marvelous substance known as Eau d'Enchant. ",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "9394b9b9-ec1f-4bd3-9a10-f9ddca047b7a",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "When you apply Eau d'Enchant to an ordinary weapon, it transforms the weapon into a magical one. This will give the weapon the potential to do greater damage and be capable of damaging magical or Undead creatures.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "0d97ceff-f7a5-468d-95bd-b94b389ea962",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "When you cast a Spark spell, you are not changing the essence of the weapon you use. The weapon is merely the mediator for your magical energy. ",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "bb980bec-c9c8-402b-a564-6ed2f9ad4162",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "If your weapon is not inherently magical, when you strike a non-corporal creature with the bespelled weapon, only the Spark damage will harm it.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "361e8b4f-b88d-42e9-bd8a-2c194fa0e4bb",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "When you use the Eau d'Enchant upon your weapon, the weapon is changed or enhanced. This is the Aspect of Alchemy - transformation.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "a41e0e52-e4f8-4741-8e31-c3296aef8f8d",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "The weapon has become magical and will continue to be so for one hour. It will do full damage against one of the insubstantial Undead.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "id": "19da2965-ec96-4a09-a70c-c7781e125b68",
                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                    "skill": "Magic",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "cf321297-acb0-4943-80cd-64feec2bb378",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions before we begin?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "1f4e66a7-1e60-4fb3-a65b-9cdfef28a5fa",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "a7ac5f88-b618-4ca3-81df-cb8f31be6b38",
                            "text": "Ask About the Professor's Background",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4a1da77a-8fb8-492e-a3ba-2c7080a1477f",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Did you always want to be a Wizard when you were a child?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "90db0da0-be9b-4440-980b-77a94f3584f0",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "My word, no, I never dreamed that I had an ounce of magical ability. I loved reading about magic... but then again, I loved reading and learning. I had hoped that I could grow up to become governess or an amanuensis.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "37b527f6-a0cb-4a57-b61a-d2731100b8c3",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "While growing up, Wizards seemed so great, powerful, wise, and wonderful to me. I was deemed silly, hopeless, featherbrained, and too much of a dreamer to accomplish anything with my life. ",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a06c8cb5-60e5-44df-b7ed-6442d71af7b1",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Of course, as a child, I believed everything that others said of me. Now I know that what I think of me is far more important than the opinion of others.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "176ea01a-1840-41a2-8e0a-9b9847aea5aa",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "60",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "18b16ab0-9618-4afe-889a-304143ad712f",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "8",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "9f5c1309-2762-478d-95bb-b31ec2798064",
                            "text": "Ask About Spark and Eau d'Enchant Combined",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "9b089001-ae75-4adb-8bb7-2db63551693f",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Can you use the Spark spell and Eau d'Enchant upon the same weapon?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "62b70db7-d90d-431f-bf10-ad734452d3dd",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Indeed, you can enchant and bespell the same weapon, even one which is already magical. The effects simply enhance one another.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "53990444-f687-4f26-841e-cb8fea41f0e0",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "60",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "1b85a9b9-9954-4b76-9234-992a044a13d3",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "027e21c2-1e20-4366-8390-9ffede8f18d7",
                            "text": "Make a Joke About Wizards",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "90b59919-5606-4293-9566-a9ebf50f323e",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Why were the other Wizards upset with the Necromancer at the Magical Arts party?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "80b0c0cd-a4ed-49e1-aeb3-ba66ce9d88c8",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I confess my ignorance. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "53b03f60-6f76-447b-96a7-fa1a7a22a4ca",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Because the Necromancer brought along his Ghoul-friend.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "832109e3-1efa-4c30-a280-6bf8e9162520",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Ah, that must be another of your little jokes. Perhaps you could try to focus upon the subjects of Alchemy and Eau d'Enchant now without the distraction of humor?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "f713c9ff-fd8d-4a44-81df-12318ce42016",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "60",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "7a67172c-8b27-4833-8be5-449e07eab35c",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "1",
                                                "change": "0",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "6dc62df0-4e3d-44d0-b742-d84d5c7273f5",
                            "text": "Say Nothing",
                            "nodes": [],
